WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: cnh

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.260
Translator: Van Cung Lian
Reviewer: TED Open Translation

00:00:16.064 --> 00:00:19.068
Upatmi nu le pa hna,
TED ahhin thithruainak le cawlcanghnak

00:00:19.092 --> 00:00:20.673
thawkning tampi kan chim ve.

00:00:20.697 --> 00:00:23.111
Cuca'h, cawlcanghnak thawkning
hram in dongh tiang

00:00:23.135 --> 00:00:24.379
minute 3 chungah zoh u sih

00:00:24.403 --> 00:00:26.236
i, cu chungin cawnnak ilak hna u sih.

00:00:26.260 --> 00:00:27.618
Ahmasaah, nan hngalh bangin

00:00:27.642 --> 00:00:31.060
hruaitu nih intuarnak
caah ralthatnak aherh.

00:00:32.723 --> 00:00:34.521
Zohmanh, a tuahmi hi zulh a fawite.

00:00:34.545 --> 00:00:36.909
Hi ahhin a zultu hmasa
nih biapi thil a tuah;

00:00:36.933 --> 00:00:39.236
Hnuzulh dan kha
hawidang a hmuhsak hna.

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:41.815
Amah cu hruaitu nih hruaitu
bangin a upat kan hmuh;

00:00:41.839 --> 00:00:43.784
Atu cu hruaitu kong asi ti lai lo;

00:00:43.808 --> 00:00:45.236
Anmah kong asi lai, atammi.

00:00:45.736 --> 00:00:47.813
Zoh, a hawidang a kawh cang hna,

00:00:47.837 --> 00:00:49.837
Nan hngalh khawh ahcun,
apakhatnak zultu

00:00:49.861 --> 00:00:53.236
zei ah rel lomi santlailo
dirhmun ah chiah asi khi.

00:00:53.260 --> 00:00:55.236
Hitin um khawh dingah ralthatnak aherh.

00:00:55.744 --> 00:01:00.236
hmasabik hruaitu khi hawidang hna
hruaitu ah sertu taktak cu asi.

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:02.236
(Nihthawng)

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:05.481
(Kutbenghthawng)

00:01:05.505 --> 00:01:07.236
Cun, tucu pahnihnak
zultu a ra cang.

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:09.658
Tucu, santlailo pahnih an um cang--

00:01:09.682 --> 00:01:12.236
Pathum cu mibu an si cang,
i mibu cu thawngpang a si.

00:01:12.260 --> 00:01:14.236
Cucaah, cawlcanghnak cu
zapi he aa san.

00:01:14.603 --> 00:01:17.836
Hruaitu lawng siloin zultu hna
hmaisuam ve zong abiapi,

00:01:17.860 --> 00:01:21.756
zeicatiah, zultuthar nih zultu hmasa
hna an izohchunh hna.

00:01:22.260 --> 00:01:24.832
Hi, an tam deuh thluahmah cang,
tlawmpal ah,

00:01:24.856 --> 00:01:26.236
mi pathum an ichap cang.

00:01:26.260 --> 00:01:28.680
Thazang a cak tuk cang,
tlauh khawh asi tilo.

00:01:28.704 --> 00:01:30.481
Tucu, cawlcanghnak a thawk cang.

00:01:30.505 --> 00:01:31.505
(Nihthawng)

00:01:31.911 --> 00:01:34.236
Si, zohhmanh, mi an tam deuh ahcun,

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:35.824
hna a ngam deuh suaumau.

00:01:35.848 --> 00:01:38.079
Tuandeuh ah a thu sasawhmi hna kha,

00:01:38.103 --> 00:01:39.613
itel ve an duh cang.

00:01:39.637 --> 00:01:42.977
An thiamtuk rih men lai lo,
nihsawh an si lai lo.

00:01:43.001 --> 00:01:45.810
nain khulhrang in an ti ahcun,
zapi lakah an itel ve ko lai.

00:01:45.834 --> 00:01:48.566
(Nihthawng)

00:01:48.590 --> 00:01:50.105
Cuticun,
minute tlawmpal hnuah,

00:01:50.129 --> 00:01:52.891
zapi lakah an ipeih
thluahmah na hmuh lai

00:01:52.915 --> 00:01:56.176
itel ve lo tu kha an duh ti lai lo.

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:58.177
Hihi cawlcanghnak thawkning cu asi.

00:01:58.201 --> 00:02:00.177
Asi, hi chungin cawnnak ilak u sih.

00:02:00.916 --> 00:02:03.236
Hmasaah, amah lawng in
a dir i ankgi loin a lammi

00:02:03.260 --> 00:02:06.236
bantuk na si ahcun.

00:02:06.260 --> 00:02:10.236
Zultu hmasa pawl kha tlukruannak in
na hruai hna aherh kha philh hlah.

00:02:10.260 --> 00:02:12.710
Afiang. Cawlcanghnak kong asi,
nangmah kong asi lo.

00:02:12.734 --> 00:02:13.796
(Nihthawng)

00:02:13.820 --> 00:02:16.336
Si, cawn/ilak ding taktak
kan hrialh sual kho men.

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:18.236
Abiapibik kan cawn hnga dingmi--

00:02:18.260 --> 00:02:19.781
na hngalh kho maw?--

00:02:19.805 --> 00:02:22.236
cu thithruainak cu thangthatnak asi.

00:02:22.989 --> 00:02:25.037
Asi, a thawk hmasatu cu angki hruklopa asi

00:02:25.061 --> 00:02:26.570
i amah cu lawmh asi ko lai,

00:02:26.594 --> 00:02:28.384
nain zulhtu hna nunthlentu taktak cu

00:02:28.408 --> 00:02:31.236
zultu hmasa khi dakaw asi.

00:02:31.748 --> 00:02:33.999
i, hruaitu kan si dih aherh
timi cawnpiaknak hi

00:02:34.023 --> 00:02:35.615
sullam a ngeih tuk then lai lo.

00:02:35.639 --> 00:02:38.043
Cawlcanghnak thawk
nai timh taktak ahcun

00:02:38.067 --> 00:02:41.236
zulh ding ralthatnak ngei law,
zulhning zong cawnpiak hna.

00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:43.874
Cun, santlailo nih thiltha
pakhatkhat an tuah ahcun,

00:02:43.898 --> 00:02:47.236
zultu tha ah ser khawh izuam colh.

00:02:47.260 --> 00:02:49.599
Cun, hibantuk tuahnak hmunhma
thabik cu TED asi.

00:02:50.027 --> 00:02:51.236
Lawmtuk.

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:53.862
Kutbenghthawng.

